{"tid":1216579,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[考古] 各大型衝突中 警察武力程度統計","createTime":"2019-06-13T10:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T10:37:54.000Z","uid":117636,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c0c8a87da90ed485b3bb8cc663789531bc3519d8","tid":1216579,"uid":117636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:26:31.000Z","msg":"1967年11月15日 六七暴動<br />\n示威者於干諾道中嘉華銀行放置五枚真炸彈，又於摩利臣街放置四枚真彈，復於上環大笪地附近放置六枚真彈。警方見狀，先後施放十枚催淚彈將暴徒驅散。<br />\n<a href=\"https://christiantimes.org.hk/Common/Reader/News/ShowNews.jsp?Nid=85890&amp;Pid=6&amp;Version=0&amp;Cid=150&amp;Charset=big5_hkscs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchristiantimes.org.hk%2FCommon%2FReader%2FNews%2FShowNews.jsp%3FNid%3D85890%26Pid%3D6%26Version%3D0%26Cid%3D150%26Charset%3Dbig5_hkscs&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmaP8PJJZD286lWcuKEclkJo%3D&h=88eae212\" target=\"_blank\">https://christiantimes.org.hk/Common/Reader/News/ShowNews.jsp?Nid=85890&amp;Pid=6&amp;Version=0&amp;Cid=150&amp;Charset=big5_hkscs</a><br />\n<br />\n2005年10月11日 韓農反世貿騷亂 (香港)<br />\n防暴警察於入夜後需要發射34枚催淚彈及6顆布袋彈驅散示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/香港反對世貿遊行衝突\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%96%E8%B2%BF%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmaP8PJJZD286lWcuKEclkJo%3D&h=1096f102\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/香港反對世貿遊行衝突</a><br />\n<br />\n2014年9月29日 雨傘運動 (香港)<br />\n是次行動中，警方使用87顆催淚彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/9&middot;28催淚彈驅散行動#發射催淚彈\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F9%C2%B728%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E9%A9%85%E6%95%A3%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%23%E7%99%BC%E5%B0%84%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmaP8PJJZD286lWcuKEclkJo%3D&h=1a3ef41c\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/9&middot;28催淚彈驅散行動#發射催淚彈</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年6月13日 金鐘衝突 (香港)<br />\n警務處處長盧偉聰及副處長鄧炳強指約使用了<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">150枚催淚彈, 數發橡膠子彈, 布袋彈, 胡椒彈等武器</span></span><br />\n<ins>他強調警員當時是生命受威脅，才迫不得已使用武力驅逐人群。</ins><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/550502/即時新聞/警方就昨日行動見記者(現場)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F550502%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%A8%E6%97%A5%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E8%A6%8B%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%28%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%29&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmaP8PJJZD286lWcuKEclkJo%3D&h=2b98535c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F550502%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%A8%E6%97%A5%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E8%A6%8B%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%28%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%29&h=a17b0604\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/550502/即時新聞/警方就昨日行動見記者(現場)</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警屌你老母</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45fc808f7c9ba769a5b84f4a8a602e51f5e6c94","tid":1216579,"uid":226955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:27:59.000Z","msg":"唔準你咁樣鬧我地英勇嘅香港警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成班反人類罪嘅蓄生準備上聯合國接受審判啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUxq7VC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUxq7VC.gif&h=721ac9a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少年於金鐘一帶背向警察站立，遭十多名速龍小隊成員<span style=\"color: red;\">強行拉扯到地上用警棍圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aQu85Ja.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaQu85Ja.gif&h=0ec58946&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少女下午於立法會地下門外落單，遭近十名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">以盾牌及警棍按倒地上瘋狂圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wk41Gxi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwk41Gxi.gif&h=5c8616cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名手無寸鐵市民於大會堂對出方向，遭4-5名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">揮棍不停攻擊頭部倒地。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/4g17BRj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4g17BRj.gif&h=509faf8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名外藉男子於愛丁堡廣場附近，因行動不便獨自坐於花槽旁，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員以胡椒噴劑近距離向臉部射擊。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLz5ovx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLz5ovx.gif&h=58851dc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i8PQzCe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi8PQzCe.gif&h=58a9a71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UvSnqJW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUvSnqJW.gif&h=c1469b1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>下午時份於金鐘天橋附近一帶，一名中年婦人向警員哭求停止對香港人使用武力，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員近距離以不明武器擊中頭部。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/d6KQzNf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6KQzNf.gif&h=b3ebd9eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名市民於金鐘橋底下，遭警員<span style=\"color: red;\">以布袋彈瞄準頭部射擊</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映：<br />\n示威者吐血<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhRCPds07zSM&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmaP8PJJZD286lWcuKE